3#ifndef __NVKM_I2C_PAD_H__
4#define __NVKM_I2C_PAD_H__
5#include <subdev/i2c.h>
6
7struct nvkm_i2c_pad {
8 const struct nvkm_i2c_pad_func *func;
9 struct nvkm_i2c *i2c;
10#define NVKM_I2C_PAD_HYBRID(n) /* 'n' is hw pad index */ (n)
11#define NVKM_I2C_PAD_CCB(n) /* 'n' is ccb index */ ((n) + 0x100)
12#define NVKM_I2C_PAD_EXT(n) /* 'n' is dcb external encoder type */ ((n) + 0x200)
13 int id;
14
15 enum nvkm_i2c_pad_mode {
16 NVKM_I2C_PAD_OFF,
17 NVKM_I2C_PAD_I2C,
18 NVKM_I2C_PAD_AUX,
19 } mode;
20 struct mutex mutex;
21 struct list_head head;
22};
23
24struct nvkm_i2c_pad_func {
25 int (*bus_new_0)(struct nvkm_i2c_pad *, int id, u8 drive, u8 sense,
26 struct nvkm_i2c_bus **);
27 int (*bus_new_4)(struct nvkm_i2c_pad *, int id, u8 drive,
28 struct nvkm_i2c_bus **);
29
30 int (*aux_new_6)(struct nvkm_i2c_pad *, int id, u8 drive,
31 struct nvkm_i2c_aux **);
32
33 void (*mode)(struct nvkm_i2c_pad *, enum nvkm_i2c_pad_mode);
34};
35
36void nvkm_i2c_pad_ctor(const struct nvkm_i2c_pad_func *, struct nvkm_i2c *,
37 int id, struct nvkm_i2c_pad *);
38int nvkm_i2c_pad_new_(const struct nvkm_i2c_pad_func *, struct nvkm_i2c *,
39 int id, struct nvkm_i2c_pad **);
40void nvkm_i2c_pad_del(struct nvkm_i2c_pad **);
41void nvkm_i2c_pad_init(struct nvkm_i2c_pad *);
42void nvkm_i2c_pad_fini(struct nvkm_i2c_pad *);
43void nvkm_i2c_pad_mode(struct nvkm_i2c_pad *, enum nvkm_i2c_pad_mode);
44int nvkm_i2c_pad_acquire(struct nvkm_i2c_pad *, enum nvkm_i2c_pad_mode);
45void nvkm_i2c_pad_release(struct nvkm_i2c_pad *);
46
47void g94_i2c_pad_mode(struct nvkm_i2c_pad *, enum nvkm_i2c_pad_mode);
48
49int nv04_i2c_pad_new(struct nvkm_i2c *, int, struct nvkm_i2c_pad **);
50int nv4e_i2c_pad_new(struct nvkm_i2c *, int, struct nvkm_i2c_pad **);
51int nv50_i2c_pad_new(struct nvkm_i2c *, int, struct nvkm_i2c_pad **);
52int g94_i2c_pad_x_new(struct nvkm_i2c *, int, struct nvkm_i2c_pad **);

58int gm204_i2c_pad_s_new(struct nvkm_i2c *, int, struct nvkm_i2c_pad **);

62#define PAD_MSG(p,l,f,a...) do { \
63 struct nvkm_i2c_pad *_pad = (p); \
64 nvkm_##l(&_pad->i2c->subdev, "pad %04x: "f"\n", _pad->id, ##a); \
65} while(0)
66#define PAD_ERR(p,f,a...) PAD_MSG((p), error, f, ##a)
67#define PAD_DBG(p,f,a...) PAD_MSG((p), debug, f, ##a)
68#define PAD_TRACE(p,f,a...) PAD_MSG((p), trace, f, ##a)
69#endif
